        <!-- PROJECT CONTENT -->
        <div class="project-content mt-5">

            <h1 class="project-title">ServeLanka</h1>
            <p class="project-subtitle">Nationwide Local Services Platform</p>

            <p class="project-description">
                <strong>ServeLanka</strong> is a nationwide local services platform designed
                to connect Sri Lankan users with service providers across multiple sectors
                such as home repairs, beauty services, transport, tourism support, freelance
                work, and emergency services. The platform enables users to easily discover,
                compare, and book trusted service providers based on location and availability.
            </p>

            <p class="project-description">
                The system aims to digitalize Sri Lanka’s largely unorganized service sector
                by offering service providers a modern digital presence while helping users
                quickly find reliable services, especially in urgent situations.
            </p>

            <!-- OBJECTIVES -->
            <h5 class="mt-4">Project Objectives</h5>
            <ul class="project-tech">
                <li>Connect users with local service providers nationwide</li>
                <li>Provide digital profiles and portfolios for service providers</li>
                <li>Enable location-based service discovery</li>
                <li>Support real-time booking and availability management</li>
                <li>Build trust through ratings, reviews, and service history</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- CORE FEATURES -->
            <h5 class="mt-4">Core Features</h5>
            <ul class="project-tech">
                <li>User and service provider registration & authentication</li>
                <li>Profile creation with photos, skills, and service details</li>
                <li>Service searching and advanced filtering</li>
                <li>Geolocation-based nearby service detection</li>
                <li>Real-time booking and availability management</li>
                <li>Ratings, reviews, and service history tracking</li>
                <li>Admin panel for platform management</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- TECHNOLOGIES -->
            <h5 class="mt-4">Technologies Used</h5>
            <ul class="project-tech">
                <li>React Native (Frontend)</li>
                <li>Node.js & Express (Backend)</li>
                <li>Firebase (Database & Authentication)</li>
                <li>Google Maps API (Location Services)</li>
                <li>Figma (UI/UX Design)</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- METHODOLOGY -->
            <h5 class="mt-4">Development Methodology</h5>
            <p class="project-description">
                The project was developed using the <strong>Agile methodology</strong>,
                enabling iterative development, continuous testing, frequent reviews,
                and flexibility for requirement changes throughout the development lifecycle.
            </p>

